Package: pvecm
Type: Package
Title: Estimate VECM for heterogeneous panels as in Canning and Pedroni (2008)
Version: 1.0
Author: Reynaldo Senra Hodelin
Maintainer: Reynaldo Senra Hodelin <reynaldosenra@gmx.com>
Description: Estimates VECM models for heterogeneous panels. It also applies long-run
    causality tests as in Canning and Pedroni (2008).
